title: 299: Elite 11 Recap; Bruce Feldman, Will Grier & Jalen Hurts interviews
itunes:title: 299: Elite 11 Recap; Bruce Feldman, Will Grier & Jalen Hurts interviews
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks build the stingiest defense possible up the middle from the best in the NFL (10:21). The guys then break down what they saw over the weekend from college football's top quarterbacks at the Elite 11 Finals (19:24). DJ then sits down with Fox's Bruce Feldman, West Virginia QB Will Grier and Bama signal caller Jalen Hurts (39:29).
